><blockquote><blockquote>其實韓戰個時都試過，法國外籍兵團入黑之後刺刀衝鋒成功收復被共軍佔領既陣地<br />\n<br />\n鴉片戰爭個時英軍都係用刺刀擊潰清兵</blockquote><br />\n個疑問係無哂子彈同全身而退<br />\n太神奇掛</blockquote><br />\n唔出奇 訓練，士氣，組織，戰術相差好遠</blockquote><br />\n如果刀咁好秋 <br />\n證明1) 佢地用刀好過用槍,幾個鐘槍戰都走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2)佢地真係ironman"},{"pid":"f04b8b57378f1003687da92600c7dd456940ebbe","tid":306551,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌,摩蘇爾既IS依家謝晒皮啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伊拉克軍隊已經收復左9成地區<br />\n<br />\n但依然有小量ISIS 繼續躲藏 抵抗"},{"pid":"9d4a985ad17686d021318ad7a31d793f700be349","tid":306551,"uid":15216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"個個john wick?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512689993d99ed344d1da9f8c041992da599181a","tid":306551,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌,摩蘇爾既IS依家謝晒皮啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伊拉克軍隊已經收復左9成地區<br />\n<br />\n但依然有小量ISIS 繼續躲藏 抵抗</blockquote><br />\n呢堆IS分分鐘都一樣無乜子彈,如果有槍,點會完全殺唔到要打近戰既SAS,係一個都無,比人打住咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504353ed849e4d703c0caf25d5bbd2bb848a8eb8","tid":306551,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解is堆人咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國佬似吹水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁好彩啲恐怖份子同時又用晒子彈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk