解is堆人咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國佬似吹水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁好彩啲恐怖份子同時又用晒子彈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定雙方既配置英軍係無撚講清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當對面唔係正式軍隊,五槍先殺到一件好未?<br />\nSAS可以全身而退真係好假,對方應該都無乜彈藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D野真係任佢地吹, 反正無人睇到, 根本無得驗證<br />\n<br />\n就好似我之前睇新聞<br />\n有一個 庫爾德女狙擊手話自己 射殺左300名ISIS<br />\n有一個伊拉克男子 話自己殺左150名ISIS<br />\n有一個老母話幫自己個仔報仇, 用AK47 殺左幾十個ISIS<br />\n<br />\n當故事睇下就算</blockquote><br />\n美軍空襲炸死晒就入自己數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無空中力量支援,打357年仲分分鐘唔係IS輸而係庫族同政府軍投降都有知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2014年<br />\n800名ISIS 攻打摩蘇爾, 打敗三萬伊拉克軍隊<br />\n仲記得好清楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fall_of_Mosul\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFall_of_Mosul&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=32618dea\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fall_of_Mosul</a>"},{"pid":"e973a92dc05a939ab459d871205dafa4d24e3dc0","tid":306551,"uid":10890,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右又係有篇報道<br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面有單傳聞<br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢"},{"pid":"5ed636d0eb521f382fa39dbbed2f0bef4e08d520","tid":306551,"uid":77029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"香港版：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國版：手撕日本鬼子<br />\n美國版：雷霆救兵<br />\n英國版：SAS 刺刀殺ISIS<br />\n<br />\n屌，連英國都玩洗腦國民教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73283b5cf8aa9c3c2d3fb5a5894789a15e0dede","tid":306551,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"不過亦都咁講<br />\nIS班友會衰係因為佢地寧舍想活捉<br />\n捉嚟直播斬首又好 虐待玩下都好<br />\n結果被人有機可乘"},{"pid":"0e5e7985ea5f478503bb76677ae8af21b5a6b91e","tid":306551,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c88a29785f97957aafc336bfaeb6913ad42fbd9","tid":306551,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過亦都咁講<br />\nIS班友會衰係因為佢地寧舍想活捉<br />\n捉嚟直播斬首又好 虐待玩下都好<br />\n結果被人有機可乘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個可能性係最大<br />\n<br />\n否則SAS 同ISIS 有一段距離既話<br />\n<br />\nSAS 未衝到去, 已經比人射死左"},{"pid":"7d3581a78621cee5adba21cb3584996598f25928","tid":306551,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a33ecfb077e51ae6cf4c8e83744be47c7300abaf","tid":306551,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到咁詳細, 又咁神勇, 十足十共軍手撕日軍咁<br />\n硬係覺得自己加左D野落去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7a7b3d51ca2dd11683bfa58c5f5f361acba9c1","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249216dc6dc9aaae4221804eb9b585ce5a05d6b1","tid":306551,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右又係有篇報道<br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面有單傳聞<br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n我當然知道 SAS 係勁<br />\n<br />\n不過如果佢地用槍 射殺10倍敵人,就好合理<br />\n<br />\n但用刀 用槍當棍 打死敵人, 就好難以置信<br />\n唯一可能性係ISIS 都想活捉SAS ,結果偷雞不成蝕渣米"},{"pid":"dc67a0b5b84442cfdfc2b31bb2cded758b9e64b9","tid":306551,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右<span style=\"color: red;\">又係有篇報道</span><br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: red;\">有單傳聞</span><br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb21dc7f254acd1619cb72ef07bab5df9978411a","tid":306551,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過亦都咁講<br />\nIS班友會衰係因為佢地寧舍想活捉<br />\n捉嚟直播斬首又好 虐待玩下都好<br />\n結果被人有機可乘</blockquote><br />\n呢個理由我buy喎</blockquote><br />\n即係好似拍戲咁用槍指人唔開槍, 然後捉唔到人就寧願拎住支槍走佬都完全唔射班英軍?"},{"pid":"27ae40aba9bdd72a15bb054a2db87cdfeeddf8cb","tid":306551,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右<span style=\"color: red;\">又係有篇報道</span><br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: red;\">有單傳聞</span><br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞嗰單冇正式媒體講過<br />\n我都只可以話係有可能兼可行<br />\n但用kukri斬3個嗰篇係出晒街"},{"pid":"ee6c30de5dd891069656304b71f3dbe9686c2e4f","tid":306551,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e85848e24dd4fd177dfec22c8ac2540498f63ce","tid":306551,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"其實打伊拉克嗰時英軍都衝過一次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F38kbv98.html&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=02f4fb79\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html</a>"},{"pid":"8d5c8f837bb340c636a4acfbd635ccf40740b322","tid":306551,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75988ac5d705bd1307dcc732f69f746698629706","tid":306551,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實打伊拉克嗰時英軍都衝過一次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F38kbv98.html&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=02f4fb79\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20個拎刀 衝向300個有槍既<br />\n結果300個有槍既 被殺左30個, 其餘逃走"},{"pid":"2cca95d19959a22e5a72c43cf39db498202d006c","tid":306551,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解is堆人咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國佬似吹水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁好彩啲恐怖份子同時又用晒子彈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定雙方既配置英軍係無撚講清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當對面唔係正式軍隊,五槍先殺到一件好未?<br />\nSAS可以全身而退真係好假,對方應該都無乜彈藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D野真係任佢地吹, 反正無人睇到, 根本無得驗證<br />\n<br />\n就好似我之前睇新聞<br />\n有一個 庫爾德女狙擊手話自己 射殺左300名ISIS<br />\n有一個伊拉克男子 話自己殺左150名ISIS<br />\n有一個老母話幫自己個仔報仇, 用AK47 殺左幾十個ISIS<br />\n<br />\n當故事睇下就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，IS都算係同世界咁多個國家為敵的組織，比d新聞講到好似好易殺咁，咁點解而加仲味比人收皮"},{"pid":"a474c41f68d09978214bfeee4270f7e58e922d81","tid":306551,"uid":105062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得要考慮返當時的地理環境同戰術<br />\n如果當時處於一直空曠地方我覺得係有Ｄ吹水成份<br />\n因為係空曠而又沒彈藥的情況下幾好武功都癈，我偏唔信30人唔夠打一隊小隊<br />\n<br />\n依班SAS係做情報收集任務，好大可能係ISIS知道要活捉佢地，一黎可以有機會獲取英國果邊的情報，二黎又可以用黎虐殺下咁。但佢地又沒考慮到地形環境，而衝動一味想生擒。所以咪咁啱比人出奇反勝"},{"pid":"21bcac22a8285a1e7953297d7e58a7c948de84ed","tid":306551,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"希望遲D拍電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fe6606858f74345e786de3e07e1c5f08d267eb","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f724b5f022b0b08162187891bc4ddc61f5ed7d","tid":306551,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"蛇叔上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1e20aadf661b32768ce9cfda88c8c8c8cb9fac","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d1139fef1e387ef1be114da0f6b9352e23e6f9","tid":306551,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562845e4f4a77b95b6d185d06d03d2fe6a92545f","tid":306551,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc75f884eb694013f5f1891d964e34e8441daec0","tid":306551,"uid":55153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右<span style=\"color: red;\">又係有篇報道</span><br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: red;\">有單傳聞</span><br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn wick咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkill three man with a funcking pencil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521524786b6055c792a4b13c60bf05794c318253","tid":306551,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b1994d7084c27eaf92c4aabc207e7156af6230","tid":306551,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右<span style=\"color: red;\">又係有篇報道</span><br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: red;\">有單傳聞</span><br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn wick咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkill three man with a funcking pencil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鉛筆同kukri差好遠喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb32298b64c45ef9ef42b85bdcf317c003007b2","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5812d8eaeae3f7d0b15e03dcb2514787b1b43021","tid":306551,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"打機咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5144ce3ba93798f8cd73f24d12202c2b497b582c","tid":306551,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:47:34.000Z","msg":"對面無槍咁<br />\n避彈衣防到近距射擊咩<br />\n<br />\n唯一可能地形多障礙，路淺<br />\n距離根本好近但雙方唔敢沖<br />\n對面可能軍備訓練麻麻，偵察兵更弱無諗過行行下草地遇到高級敵人<br />\nDead man tell no tale"},{"pid":"d482474bf966df1d7dc5ac868b63bb4ae361d5bd","tid":306551,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"比起L85,用刺刀係順手好多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7909c6d184e809049a44fd684a90703eaa6b71","tid":306551,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比起L85,用刺刀係順手好多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSAS 應該唔係用sa80"},{"pid":"11806873762f7f4147a1aff472b5fda45c0542b1","tid":306551,"uid":93027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"Call of Duty Ghost 一開頭情節來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0da25f2e87941c82442e19122456c83766a7175","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134ba131d974e53e9fb1ae01742425b084c4dd38","tid":306551,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"班 is 想活捉人咪被人反 cup 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10b038306997d01450883b1b1ce5d4626340cbd","tid":306551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5051876e046bf7d739a5352a4c787025b6c2eb6","tid":306551,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0