"msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意返,係用槍射死左20個先, 先得返10發子彈, 之後先肉搏, TOTAL 先殺左32個, 唔係一下肉搏殺左32個<br />\n<br />\n第二, 呢隊野人數究竟係幾多?我諗係6-7個, IS當時得返30人, 佢地都以為對方仲有子彈, 所以先會怯, 唔需要幻想到D乜, 純粹係突然對方發難先會輸到咁<br />\n<br />\n當時英軍訓練都係好勁, 加埋背水一戰的心態, 一人殺2件都唔奇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一方面 要活捉對方，一方面係垂死掙扎，此消彼長下有呢個戰果真係唔出奇"},{"pid":"eb72ca4086519a2e07691f00e001feee6e2caedf","tid":306551,"uid":35069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"講真，唔會完全無晒子彈先衝過去，如果真有其事，自己設身處地諗，好可能係一邊靠掩護射擊，一邊搵人衝上去，將大部分子彈交俾負責掩護既人，一班就係射擊下儘量搵掩體衝上去，期間衝果班又可以做靶，俾到短時間機會做掩護果班射班isis，其後混戰前面果班開始肉搏，後面果班再衝上黎幫手。咁樣既話都可以有理由相信既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2479685265030e2bff5a8643113fa03b75b6b1b8","tid":306551,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實打伊拉克嗰時英軍都衝過一次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F38kbv98.html&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=02f4fb79\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/38kbv98.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20個拎刀 衝向300個有槍既<br />\n結果300個有槍既 被殺左30個, 其餘逃走</blockquote><br />\n難道英國用左強化人士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f72edb7d0205317eaff51e091121c809654fc8a","tid":306551,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"係都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n殺紅左眼 腎上線素急升 暫時無痛覺<br />\n<br />\n再加上背水一戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都係敢死隊"},{"pid":"b2ac415b7bba236eba3854d68840a7bc1a018cb7","tid":306551,"uid":55153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為全球第一支正規特種部隊<br />\nSAS出晒名係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱仔成最愛嘅SDU都係跟SAS嘅訓練出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時候左右<span style=\"color: red;\">又係有篇報道</span><br />\n話有個SAS member喺用晒彈之後<br />\n直接掹把kukri出嚟<br />\n第一刀將一個IS恐怖分子斬頭<br />\n第二刀割咗第二個恐怖分子喉<br />\n第三刀又殺左一個<br />\n之後再斬傷3個<br />\n斬到人地走夾唔抖<br />\n<br />\n上面<span style=\"color: red;\">有單傳聞</span><br />\n話有個US army ranger同恐怖分子肉搏戰嗰陣<br />\n想用刀但發覺kick住掹唔出<br />\n結果就咁用佢隨身帶住嘅MRE膠匙羹<br />\n係咁捅個恐怖分子條頸<br />\n就咁捅死咗佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\njohn wick咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkill three man with a funcking pencil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鉛筆同kukri差好遠喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n膠匙羹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff605c6e7e6cd148e303dff2195b702d5ea0044","tid":306551,"uid":55153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，唔會完全無晒子彈先衝過去，如果真有其事，自己設身處地諗，好可能係一邊靠掩護射擊，一邊搵人衝上去，將大部分子彈交俾負責掩護既人，一班就係射擊下儘量搵掩體衝上去，期間衝果班又可以做靶，俾到短時間機會做掩護果班射班isis，其後混戰前面果班開始肉搏，後面果班再衝上黎幫手。咁樣既話都可以有理由相信既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger 仲有10粒彈應該交左比一兩個人cover先沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa3822f8482c0da7752ec1a37f328e320988edb","tid":306551,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話假嗰啲應該未知SAS係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />